cates are formed. These results have\nbeen corroborated with Scanning Electron Microscopy results which clearly show\nthe early changes in the morphology of the hydrated C3S due to nanosilica\nincorporation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 May 2021 09:41:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-01"}
